      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STIFLER (8) is yet to be beaten at the course and distance, scoring three wins from as many starts. Comes off a (16.75) win last time, scoring by 3.5 lengths in a Invitation over 300m at this track. Rates on top and should go close. JUKEBOX DUKE (1) was safely held last time out, finishing fifth at Gawler over 400m behind Mad Maverick (23.17) in a OPEN. Was a winner prior to that. Should be in this for a long way. AMRON TIGER (4) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing fourth (23.21) at Gawler in a Invitation. Rates a winning chance on best. LET'S GO SAM (2) did a good job to finish second last time out over 300m at this track (17.00) in a Invitation, the second top-three finish on the trot.",
